Title: Value Investing Anomaly Detection & Dividend Analysis
Author: Samuel Castillo
AuthorUrl: https://github.com/sdcastillo
License: GPL-3
DisplayMode: Showcase
Tags: finance, stocks, anomaly-detection, dividends, value-investing, time-series
Type: Shiny
Description: Interactive dashboard for detecting stock price anomalies using ARIMA modeling 
    and analyzing dividend histories for value investing strategies. Features include 
    anomaly detection with customizable sensitivity, historical dividend tracking, and 
    comparative dividend yield analysis across multiple tickers.